nodes.body: @linus-md We definitely don't want the Dirac file to be in the branch!
@b-mehta I See, I was wondering what happened.
I just pushed a few sorries for you to prove. Do you mind trying them?
I would like this PR merged. Are the sorries the only thing that is blocking it? If so, should I attempt them?

Yeah, I cleaned up already once, so the sorries are the most blocking part. Please also merge master and ensure CI passes.

This PR was written during the Bonn workshop last September and I believe the original authors have gone to do other things, so feel free to take over!
It seems I don't have push access to this branch. Could that be right? Could I get the access rights?

It would be good to coordinate with @linus-md, @rishicomplex, and @b-mehta to be sure that they would appreciate this PR being dusted off and continued (I assume they would, but it's more polite to check rather than assume!)

For getting push access @LodeVermeulen, please go to Zulip [and request write access](https://leanprover.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/287929-mathlib4/topic/github.20permission).
I would be very happy if this gets finished! @LodeVermeulen @kmill
